physically tap the multi-function button if you want. To make calls, you can simply voice phone commands, including &#34;redial&#34; or &#34;call back&#34; to get your last in-coming call once again.","You can connect two phones to the BlueAnt S4 and toggle between them if you happen to be on a call on one when another call arrives. You can answer calls on either phone and use call waiting. However, if you make a call, it will go out on the primary phone, which is phone that you connected to the BlueAnt S4 first. In addition, the primary phone is the only one that plays music employing the A2DP profile.","You will have to take one hand off the steering wheel to adjust volume controls, but that can be simply a momentary effort, since all you do is swipe your finger across the top of the device. If you prefer, you can adjust the volume by pushing and holding the volume up or volume down symbols.","The best feature of this BlueAnt S4 is its voice command setup. After you say, &#34;BlueAnt, speak to me,&#34; it will respond with, &#34;Say a command.&#34; At that point you can ask whether you&#39;re connected, instruct the phone to call back (to re-call the last phone call you got), check battery and access favorites. The device can also call the Bing 411 service that gives you these categories: information, sports, movies, navigate, weather, stock quotes, traffic or news.","The BlueAnt S4 has a sleek design with a glossy black finish and well-positioned controls for quick on-the-road access. The speaker is located in prime position for superb sound quality.","This Bluetooth car kit features two touch-sensitive volume controls at the top, a multi-function button, three lights that serve as the battery indicator, a Bluetooth indicator, a hands-free trigger indicator and a microphone. The on/off switch is located on the side next to the charging port.","You attach this compact speakerphone to your car visor using metal clips that employ two powerful magnets. The manufacturer offers a couple of different clips with this device so you can pick the best one for your visor. You also get a car charger and a rather short USB cable."]},"id":"45205841-bb30-49b9-96bc-bb6efa6a40f1","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"3aa0fdec-0e6b-4446-bdac-45b4d22ba528","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The BlueAnt S4 Bluetooth car kit presents a great set of features that will keep your eyes on the road and, in most cases, your hands safely on the wheel. This Bluetooth car kit is a superior choice if you need easy voice dialing, text-to-speech and voice answer capabilities for your communication with the rest of the world while you&#39;re on the road."]},"id":"3a740951-7e1b-432b-8fd8-934cf3b556ca","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_51439","url":"/blueant-s4-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"jeph-preece","url":"/author/jeph-preece","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Jeph Preece","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"UEqrRM5xmXnCHCjkbS6o5e","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-11-22T20:39:44Z","datePublished":"2010-11-22T20:39:44Z","name":"BlueAnt S4","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from viewing as part of this site because it has been discontinued. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","review":{"rating":98,"verdict":"With A2DP streaming audio, voice prompts and excellent help and support, this Bluetooth car kit is one of the best. ","pros":["The BlueAnt S4 gives you hands-free phone calling and receiving. It also is easy to use."],"cons":["Not all features will work with all phones. For example, if your Bluetooth-enabled phone does not permit automatic pairing, you will need to manually pair your phone and synchronize your phone book."]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from viewing as part of this